cmdjy88b40322sbrcsn4tfvqm	Like A Bottle In The Smoke (E-Book)	Like A Bottle\r\\n\r\\nIn The\r\\n\r\\nSmoke\r\\n\r\\nFrom a humble background, Obi's life was nothing different from the daily experience of an average child in his community; a neighborhood you have to strive extra hard to raise your head. Clearly exceptional among his mates, Obi struggled to keep the testament of morals strong.\r\\n\r\\nBut would virtues help him in a clime where children in the neighborhood would rather compromise to rise? It is the trial of greatness in the crucible of affliction.\r\\n\r\\nAbout the Author\r\\n\r\\n'Deji Dania is an author with a bias for children's books, and he has published quite a number both in comic and storybook genres. In addition to that, he has authored two others for adult readers with three new ones at publishing stage.\r\\n\r\\nHe is a 1992 graduate of Fine Arts from the Obafemi Awolowo University, Ile-Ife, Nigeria.\r\\n\r\\nBesides writing, as a multi-faceted creative artist, he is also an illustrator, cartoonist, graphic designer, poet, publishing consultant and contemporary visual artist. He is married with children and lives in Lagos with his family.\r\\n\r\\nACCESSIBLE PUBLISHERS LTO\r\\n\r\\nformerty Rasmed Publications Ltd\r\\n\r\\n&nbsp;	800	100	[{"public_id": null, "secure_url": "http://accessiblepublishers.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/like-a-bottle-front.jpg"}]	cmdjwh6rm0000sb2qdvkmpwaf	\N	e_book	t	active	\N	\N	\N	DEJI DANIA	\N	\N	2025-07-26 07:48:48.784	2025-07-26 07:48:48.784	f	15503	EL0000202	\N	\N	f	f	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	984
